'''Tempest''' was a form of [[Spice/Legends|spice]] produced by the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] [[Mika Anjiliac Chiera]] in the year [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]]. It was a combination of [[Glitterstim/Legends|glitterstim]] and a virus from [[Varl/Legends|Varl]], the original Hutt home world. The spice was known to have circulated through the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]] and through [[Hutt Space/Legends|Hutt Space]]. Addicts were marked by a darkening of the blood vessels and fits of uncontrollable rage.<ref name="Scourge">[[Scourge (novel)|''Scourge'']]</ref>

